# Foot Terminal

## Scrollback
# Scroll up/down (page)
Shift+PageUp/PageDown

# Scroll to top/bottom
Shift+Home/End

## Search
# Search scrollback (reverse)
Ctrl+Shift+r

# In search: next/previous match
Ctrl+r / Ctrl+s

# In search: cancel
Escape

# In search: confirm (exit at match)
Enter

## Copy/Paste
# Copy selection
Ctrl+Shift+c

# Paste clipboard
Ctrl+Shift+v

# Primary paste (middle-click equivalent)
Shift+Insert

## Font Size
# Increase
Ctrl++

# Decrease
Ctrl+-

# Reset
Ctrl+0

## URLs
# Activate URL mode (hint overlay)
Ctrl+Shift+o

# In URL mode: type hint characters to open link

## Unicode Input
# Enter unicode input mode (type hex codepoint + Enter)
Ctrl+Shift+u

## Spawning
# New terminal (inherits CWD via foot-spawn.sh)
Mod+Enter (sway binding)

# foot-spawn: opens in last tracked directory
# CWD tracked via $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR/foot-last-cwd

## Prompt Navigation (requires shell integration)
# Jump to previous prompt
Ctrl+Shift+z

# Jump to next prompt
Ctrl+Shift+x

## Miscellaneous
# Fullscreen (via Sway)
Mod+f

## Config
# Config file
~/.config/foot/foot.ini

# Colors (auto-generated by tinty)
~/.config/foot/colors.ini

# Reload config (no restart needed)
# foot watches config and reloads on change
